                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18201028-150-off809 t18201028-150-crimeloc812"></join>. On the 27th of October, the prisoner came and bought a trifle. He came again, asked for a small article, and then for silk handkerchiefs. I shewed him some but he bought none. I missed one, and found it in his trowsers.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I used my handkerchief, and put this into my trowsers thinking it was my own.</p>
